{"tid":2128493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衛生人員要求海牙國際法庭調查政府處理疫情手法！！！","createTime":"2020-07-28T04:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T05:28:01.000Z","uid":48081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0fe1af49bdbf7441b70a34bf686ecb8b0faa0a","tid":2128493,"uid":48081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">巴西</span>衛生人員要求國際法庭調查博爾索納羅處理疫情手法  <br />\n<br />\n巴西一批衛生保健人員，要求海牙國際刑事法庭，調查巴西總統博爾索納羅處理當地新型冠狀病毒疫情的手法。<br />\n<br />\n提出要求的衛生保健人員，宣稱代表一百萬同業，他們向國際刑事法庭提交資料，指控巴西政府漠視疫情，導致成千上萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n巴西政府暫時未有回應。博爾索納羅之前一再指疫情威脅不大，並忽視社交距離，要求各地暫停實施封鎖措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%8D%9A%E7%88%BE%E7%B4%A2%E7%B4%8D%E7%BE%85%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%89%8B%E6%B3%95-230343552.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25B3%2595-230343552.html&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=6e3c1b0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%8D%9A%E7%88%BE%E7%B4%A2%E7%B4%8D%E7%BE%85%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%89%8B%E6%B3%95-230343552.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd3997b6694a6a9597014b4dd520ffe9308052a","tid":2128493,"uid":48081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:22:32.